1
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:05,920
Did you think I couldn't find you if you hid?

2
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,240
My work is stressful enough.

3
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,919
And you still make trouble for me every day.

4
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,120
Always yelling about a divorce.

5
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,720
Are you seeing someone else?

6
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,440
No, I'm not.

7
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,360
No, no.

8
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,620
Don't let me catch you.

9
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,200
How dare you resist!

10
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:43,320
Let me ask you one thing.

11
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,280
Still want a divorce?

12
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,800
No.

13
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,440
No.

14
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,840
Divorce?

15
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,800
Don't even think about getting rid of me.

16
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,280
You follow wherever I go.

17
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,320
Who is it?

18
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,800
Sir, your package.

19
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,480
Just leave it at the front desk.

20
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,740
This requires your signature in person.

21
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:01,600
Honey.

22
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,680
I won't hit you anymore.

23
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,320
But if you run away again,

24
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,960
I will kill you.

25
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,600
Why do you still smell so good?

26
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,570
Wait for me a moment.

27
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,159
That's what happened.

28
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,159
She was afraid of being controlled by Li Ting again.

29
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:56,200
So before Li Ting woke up,

30
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,690
she had to strike first.

31
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,000
I see.

32
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,760
That explains

33
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:05,400
why there were signs of a second impact on his head.

34
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:05,880
Exactly.

35
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,800
But...

36
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:09,000
What does this have to do with Dong Shan?

37
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,520
Why would he help Lu Chen?

38
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,600
Captain Zhuang.

39
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,660
I found something.

40
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:14,160
Look.

41
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,640
I found this

42
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,360
in Dong Shan's factory.

43
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:31,040
He secretly took all the photos in here.

44
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,000
This might be

45
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,920
the reason he helped Lu Chen.

46
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,680
You secretly took so many photos of Lu Chen.

47
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,720
Did she know?

48
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,720
What was your purpose in doing this?

49
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:01,560
Is this behavior any different from Li Ting's?

50
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,810
No different at all.

51
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,040
Very perverted.

52
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,160
I am not like him.

53
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,240
How so?

54
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,840
I am sincere towards Xiao Lu.

55
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,520
You don't know,

56
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,080
nor did you see

57
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:16,400
how Xiao Lu was tortured by Li Ting.

58
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,080
A life worse than death,

59
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,240
covered in bruises.

60
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,520
For a scumbag like him,

61
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,850
dying a hundred times wouldn't be enough.

62
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,680
Brother Shao.

63
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:34,600
Oh.

64
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,280
Downstairs at Lu Chen's place,

65
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,200
we found that cleaner's uniform.

66
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,610
And the clothes she wore during the crime,

67
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,680
which still had Li Ting's blood on them.

68
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:54,120
Dong Shan, the evidence is conclusive now.

69
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,280
Don't hide it anymore.

70
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,920
I can see you really wanted Li Ting dead.

71
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,680
I can also see you love her very much.

72
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:04,620
That day you deliberately led us to the dark room

73
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,800
to speak out for Lu Chen,

74
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,560
didn't you?

75
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,360
Today is your best chance.

76
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:14,000
Lu Chen definitely cannot escape the charges.

77
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,560
But if you can tell the whole truth,

78
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:19,700
maybe I can fight for a lighter sentence for her.

79
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,600
Can I trust you?

80
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,720
You can only trust me.

81
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,560
Okay.

82
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,520
I'll tell you.

83
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,460
I'll tell you everything.

84
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,520
I'm a private detective.

85
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,640
Six months ago,

86
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,400
Li Ting hired me

87
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,320
to find his missing wife, Lu Chen.

88
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,610
All expenses were covered.

89
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,840
It was a lucrative job.

90
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,320
Boss Li.

91
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,720
Mr. Dong.

92
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:08,960
Well,

93
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,300
it's like this.

94
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:12,680
My wife and I just had an argument.

95
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,880
She even turned off her phone.

96
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:17,000
I really can't get in touch with her.

97
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:17,880
With this kind of thing,

98
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,760
I can't exactly contact her friends.

99
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,120
I don't want to wash our dirty linen in public.

100
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,640
I understand.

101
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:24,840
So please, I really need your help to find her.

102
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,440
Here's the thing.

103
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:28,880
We don't usually take this kind of job.

104
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,440
My wife,

105
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,120
is very naive.

106
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,280
I'm really worried something might happen to her.

107
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,880
I just want to find her now.

108
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,400
This job might be small,

109
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,680
but...

110
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:42,360
The fee won't be small.

111
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,080
This is the deposit.

112
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,160
Here is the information.

113
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,280
Wait for my good news.

114
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,420
I searched for a long time.

115
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,720
I finally found her.

116
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:05,000
She is so beautiful,

117
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,360
like sunshine.

118
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:11,040
I suddenly had a selfish urge

119
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,840
to possess her.

120
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,360
But ultimately,

121
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,440
I chose to rationally

122
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:19,080
complete this mission.

123
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,280
Boss.

124
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,370
We found the person.

125
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,680
But I never expected

126
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,440
that my action

127
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:35,480
would bring a terrible disaster upon her.

128
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,640
Let me go!

129
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,000
Still trying to run?

130
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,120
Let go.

131
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,000
Help me.

132
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:43,760
Come here!

133
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,760
Let go!

134
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,240
Come here!

135
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:48,760
Help!

136
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,600
You run.

137
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,180
Like running, huh?

138
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,920
Run again and I'll kill you.

139
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,280
Mr. Li.

140
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:55,460
Ignore her.

141
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,800
Help me.

142
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,160
Here.

143
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:57,690
Count it.

144
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,400
Mr. Li.

145
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,800
When you first came to me,

146
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,360
didn't you say

147
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,090
it was just a couple's quarrel?

148
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,400
Please.

149
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,640
What do you mean?

150
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,920
She's my wife.

151
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,480
I can do whatever I want.

152
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,160
Just do your job.

153
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:12,760
Don't meddle in my family affairs.

154
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:14,360
Let me go.

155
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,600
Be quiet!

156
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,000
I know I did something wrong.

157
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,060
I want to make up for it.

158
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,880
But

159
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,760
he hid her away.

160
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,130
I was always worried about her.

161
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:44,120
So I went to the hotel where Li Ting stayed

162
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:46,050
and applied to be a security guard.

163
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,720
I wanted to find

164
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,120
some clues about her.

165
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,840
Hello.

166
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,640
Is this Xinmai Hotel?

167
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,330
Are you still hiring security guards?

168
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:57,740
I successfully got a job at the hotel.

169
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,160
But I rarely saw Li Ting,

170
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,120
let alone Lu.

171
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,920
Until

172
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,120
that day.
